content.text:
Main honestly admit karta hoon ki maine apne bhai, behen, aur apne second phone se referral program join kiya. Mera maqsad sirf unko crypto se introduce karna tha aur unki first trade ke liye maine khud se unhe deposit bhi kiya (around $1–2) taki wo trading seekh sakein. Mera kabhi bhi referral fraud karne ka irada nahi tha.

 Mujhe pehle yeh nahi pata tha ki ek hi ghar ke multiple accounts se referral lena rules against hai. Ab main strictly ek hi account use karunga aur family ko alag se independent trading sikhane ki koshish karunga.

 Kya aap meri main account ko restore kar sakte hain? Main genuinely KuCoin ka user hoon aur long-term trade karna chahta hoon. Please help.&quot;
